      "metadata": {
        "title": "The Bitcoin Nova Podcast",
        "description": "Staci drives Bitcoin education through raw, human centered conversation. Known for translating real world moments into clear, relatable insights on Bitcoin adoption and self custody, she brings clarity without jargon or fear. As host of The Bitcoin Nova Podcast, Staci delivers thoughtful, unfiltered interviews focused on Bitcoin, energy, sovereignty, and the future of money. Her work emphasizes honest dialogue, community engagement, and practical understanding over noise. Staci is also active in grassroots Bitcoin advocacy and regularly supports community discussions and educational spaces.",
        "profileDescription": "Staci drives Bitcoin education through raw, human centered conversation. Known for translating real world moments into clear, relatable insights on Bitcoin adoption and self custody, she brings clarity without jargon or fear. As host of The Bitcoin Nova Podcast, Staci delivers thoughtful, unfiltered interviews focused on Bitcoin, energy, sovereignty, and the future of money. Her work emphasizes honest dialogue, community engagement, and practical understanding over noise. Staci is also active in grassroots Bitcoin advocacy and regularly supports community discussions and educational spaces.",
